WEBVTT

00:01.955 --> 00:04.623
Yasuho works as a delivery person at Sagawa Express,...

00:04.730 --> 00:07.604
...one of the largest transportation companies in Japan...

00:07.772 --> 00:12.447
...with more than 50,000 employees spread across 400 offices throughout the country.

00:12.621 --> 00:15.867
Oh, she's changed into her Sagawa uniform, looking sharp.

00:16.232 --> 00:19.049
Okay, she's eating a chocolate chip cookie for breakfast.

00:19.160 --> 00:21.830
Pocari sweat is a popular sports drink in Japan.

00:21.925 --> 00:24.964
This is the go-to drink when Japanese want to quickly get hydrated.

00:25.708 --> 00:29.100
So, this is the main Sagawa shipping terminal in the Tokyo area...

00:29.193 --> 00:31.523
...and where all shipments are sorted every morning.

00:31.742 --> 00:34.822
She needs to pick up the boxes which go to our specific delivery area..

00:34.965 --> 00:36.624
...and load them into her micro van.

